Just guessing:

- verify that your `svn` client runs from the command line with your working copy; 
- verify your `Settings > Team > Subversion > Path to …`;
- try opening the projects _after_ NetBeans starts;
- see also [_Using Subversion in Apache NetBeans_](https://netbeans.apache.org/tutorial/main/kb/docs/ide/subversion/#_setting_up_subversion).

