svn command line works fine;
after Netbeans successfully opened, the subversion works fine too;
opening projects after NetBeans starts also freeze the Netbeans sometimes;

this problem occurred while starting NetBeans and opening a svn project.
and i'm sure that won't happen when the network offline.
